ID":"61H35","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户B向表1中插入一条数据x，提交事务。"},"2":{"ID":"RK9BJ","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A查询表1中的数据。 "},"3":{"ID":"I9678","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户B向表1中插入一条数据y，提交事务。"},"4":{"ID":"3V318","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A查询表1中的数据。 "},"5":{"ID":"1J7MW","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A提交事务。对用户A的这次事务来说，前后两次的查询结果是不同的。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"一个事务内的两个相同查询却返回了不同数据，就是不可重复读。不可重复读对应的是修改，即INSERT或者UPDATE操作。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"不可重复读"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"问题"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"一个会话只能读取其他事务已提交的更新结果，否则，发生等待，但是其他会话可以修改这个事务中被读取的记录，而不必等待事务结束，显然，在这种隔离级别下，一个事务中的两个相同的读取操作，其结果可能不同。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"读已提交"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"READ COMMITTED"},"2":{"ID":"LR82K","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"9278P","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"2O2JI","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"C4SRR","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"61R1V","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"43884","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"4TH11","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A开启一个事务。 "},"1":{"ID":"U4982","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户B向表1中插入一条数据x，提交事务。 "},"2":{"ID":"OGA4P","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A查询表1中的数据，判断是否存在数据x。 "},"3":{"ID":"9427T","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A发现表1中没有数据x，然后也插入数据x。 "},"4":{"ID":"08O10","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"用户A提交事务，如果表中有唯一键，那么就会报错。 "},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"所谓幻读，指的是当某个事务在读取某个范围内的记录时，另外一个事务中又在该范围插入了新的记录，当之前的事务再次读取该范围的记录时，会产生幻行（Phantom row）。幻读问题对应的是插入，即INSERT操作。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"幻读"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"问题"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"在开始读取数据（事务开启）时，不再允许修改操作。在一个事务中，如果在两次相同条件的读取操作之间没有添加记录的操作，也没有其他更新操作导致在这个查询条件下记录数增多，则两次读取结果相同。换句话说，就是在一个事务中第一次读取的记录保证不会在这个事务期间发生改动。SQL Server是通过在整个事务期间给读取的记录加锁实现这种隔离级别的，这样，在这个事务结束前，其他会话不能修改事务中读取的记录，而只能等待事务结束，但是SQL Server不会阻碍其他会话向表中添加记录，也不阻碍其他会话修改其他记录。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"可重复读"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"REPEATABLE READ"},"3":{"ID":"M9VXH","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"LQ66L","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"284X5","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"在一个事务中，读取操作的结果是在这个事务开始之前其他事务就已经提交的记录，SQL Server通过在整个事务期间给表加锁实现这种隔离级别。在这种隔离级别下，对这个表的所有DML操作都是不允许的，即要等待事务结束，这样就保证了在一个事务中的两次读取操作的结果肯定是相同的。SQL标准所定义的默认事务隔离级别是SERIALIZABLE。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"序列化"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"SERIALIZABLE"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"隔离性"},"1":{"ID":"5Y1NU","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"QF048","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"8DNU9","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"select @@global.tx_isolation, @@tx_isolation;  "},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"查询隔离级别"},"1":{"ID":"5FBDC","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"H7C85","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"set session tx_isolation='read-uncommitted';"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"更改会话的隔离级别"},"2":{"ID":"54BMU","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"CT0OZ","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"set global tx_isolation='read-uncommitted';"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"更改系统的隔离级别"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"MySQL默认隔离级别"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"Isolation"},"3":{"ID":"C5HL7","lineColorHex":"#BF58F5","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"87530"