库进行了分库）"},"1":{"ID":"1WCCL","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"RPZC2","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"解决方案"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"主库备库分库方式不同（分库的规则不一样）"},"2":{"ID":"77OU2","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"39F4W","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"516L3","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"PR545","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"数据分发平台的内部是一个个的处理管道，左侧是一个个输入数据源，右侧是一个个输出数据源。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"构建通用的平台来管理和控制数据的变更。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"解决方案"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"复制到其他数据库（比如搜索引擎等）"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"主从库非对称"},"1":{"ID":"LKLVP","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","shrink":true,"objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"8TGW2","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","children":{"0":{"ID":"2J466","lineColorHex":"#DC306C","objectClass":"MindNode","text":"开始数据迁移时，记录增量日志，迁移结束后，再处理增量数据（的日志）。处理增量日志是一个逐渐收敛的过程，因为在处理过程中又会有新的增量日志进来。等到所有增量日志差不多处理完毕，锁定数据库的写操作，保证所有增量日志处理完毕之后再放开，完成整个数据迁移工作。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"不停机扩缩容"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"数据平滑迁移"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"数据复制"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"实践"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"方便应用进行数据读写的抽象层，在这个层上解决各个应用通用的访问数据库的问题。","shrink":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"数据（访问）层"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"分层架构","shrink":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YXLW6","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"WJVBZ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"SFPOJ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ZBWEN","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"R2BKX","text":"扩展性不够：无法满足高并发情况下的业务需求。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"单机数据库写请求量大量增加，导致数据库压力变大，数据库一旦挂了，那么整个业务都挂了。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RKKWN","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"OYIBD","text":"开发效率低：所有的开发在一个项目改代码，递交代码相互等待，代码冲突不断。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RNSUF","text":"代码维护难：代码功能耦合在一起，新人不知道从何下手。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"VBKQG","text":"部门越来越多，该哪个部门改动大项目中的哪个东西，撕逼的厉害。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"业务代码越来越多，都在一个GIT里，越来越难以维护；代码腐化严重、臭味越来越浓。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"MHFQQ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PFDUS","text":"部署不灵活：构建时间长，任何小修改必须重新构建整个项目，这个过程往往很长。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"上线越来越频繁，经常是一个小功能的修改，就要整个大项目要重新编译。"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"LKTBK","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"AJCCI","text":"稳定性不高：一个微不足道的小问题，可以导致整个应用挂掉。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"其他一些外围系统直接连接数据库，导致一旦数据库结构发生变化，所有的相关系统都要通知，甚至对修改不敏感的系统也要通知。"},"4":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"CEDYU","text":"每个应用服务器需要开通所有的权限、网络、FTP、各种各样的，因为每个服务器部署的应用都是一样的。"},"5":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"KTOWV","text":"作为架构师，我已经失去了对这个系统的把控......"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"单体服务的问题","shrink":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"SHKOR","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"CYVKE","text":"微服务在我国的百度搜索指数展示，自 2013 前后微服务开始逐渐被大家关注，随时间推移搜索的人也越来越多，直至 2016 年爆发。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YORVL","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"KAIES","text":"互联网技术架构飞速演进，特别是底层硬件及芯片技术快速发展，后端服务器的能力越来越强大。多数情况下，单个业务已很难消耗完一整台服务器的资源或处理能力。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"JMZVW","text":"移动互联网深度融合与应用，瘦客户端兴起，使得云端能力与承载变得更加重要。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ANLGP","text":"容器技术得到广泛认可与应用，轻量级协议、代码管理、新集成方法与工具等技术也越来越成熟。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的快速发展并广泛流行，和以下因素息息相关：","shrink":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"JAGEK","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"FQVHM","text":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3QVmvRF3-8vE1ppuN_GKVA"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"一个单体服务发展成微服务架构的历程"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的兴起背景","shrink":true,"remark":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7bVQR6uK3hKU0T77oXNJjA","remarkDisplay":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PU2VM","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ODOPY","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"EBGNK","text":"","imageName":"s_Y53KKP0RAI.jpg","imageSize":{"objectClass":"CGSize","width":318,"height":480}},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"生态图"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RGDLQ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"NLMQS","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"L4E5R","text":"Spring Boot & Cloud"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RORHO","text":"只是 Dev 层的框架，缺少 DevOps 的整体解决方案。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"基于SDK的微服务"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"第一代微服务框架"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PWGDO","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"0EOC5","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"Q4BP5","text":"Service Mesh (网格)"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"基于Agent的微服务"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"下一代微服务"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的主流技术","shrink":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"发展史","shrink":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"CAW68","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"Q9536","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YG875","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"C7K3X","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"BJI60","text":"Adrian Cockcroft"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务是细粒度的SOA。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"N5MN0","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YG0QO","text":"Tony Pujals"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务是自包含的轻量进程，他们通过HTTP(REST API)进行通信，用相对较小的工作量来创建和部署，集中有限领域的API提供给它们的使用者。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务是面向服务架构的轻量级的风格。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"18NAF","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"NFFU8","text":"SOA以企业为中心，而微服务则以应用程序为中心。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XJ2NS","text":"在微服务中，每个应用程序都被构造成一个小型服务的集合，围绕一个业务域建模。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"K8PIW","text":"该体系结构使用应用程序编程接口（API）层而不是中间件，并且协议是轻量级的。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"随着云计算时代的发展，更高粒度的微服务架构（MSA）已经从早期的SOA发展而来。","remark":"https://www.oschina.net/translate/microservices-vs-soa","remarkDisplay":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"841SM","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"MJRR4","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"9255O","text":"企业服务总线（Enterprise Service Bus，ESB）允许服务提供者和服务使用者之间进行各种点对点连接。服务可以由多个开发团队创建，但每个团队都需要了解通用的通信机制。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"SOA定义了一个提供者层（包括系统中的所有服务）和一个使用者层，或者消费者（如用户或其他服务）与系统交互的点。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"WQT52","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"6RJJ8","text":"MSA使得开发现有服务的新版本更加容易和快速。这个架构符合DevOps的最佳实践。此外，根据负载要求，服务可以独立扩展。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"在MSA中，小型的、独立的进程在高度粒度和敏捷的应用程序中相互通信。每个服务能够独立部署，这意味着服务能够在不影响整个系统的情况下被下线。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"SOA和微服务都通过用更容易管理的模块化组件替换旧的单体结构来简化软件开发。","remark":"https://www.oschina.net/translate/microservices-vs-soa","remarkDisplay":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的定义","shrink":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"5F85D","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"SXYYI","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XSTPO","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YIFWW","text":"虽然功能总量不变，但应用程序已被分解为可管理的模块或服务。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"TFGIU","text":"微服务架构强化了应用模块化的水平，而这通过单体代码库很难实现"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XD6PV","text":"因此，微服务开发的速度要快很多，更容易理解和维护。"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"IHQYL","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RVFRG","text":"单个服务更易理解、方便开发与维护。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"小点"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"首先，它解决了复杂性问题。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"TAQXT","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PNJFI","text":"只要符合服务 API 契约，开发人员可以自由选择开发技术。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"VZUMR","text":"这就意味着开发人员可以采用新技术编写或重构服务，由于服务相对较小，所以这并不会对整体应用造成太大影响。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"BESAW","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"I5K3B","text":"实现跨团队的解耦"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"TTMTI","text":"技术选择更加自由"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"小点"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"其次，这种体系结构使得每个服务都可以由专注于此服务的团队独立开发。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XPSWL","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"OUCOC","text":"开发人员无需协调对服务升级或更改的部署。这些更改可以在测试通过后立即部署。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"FSJFX","text":"所以微服务架构也使得 CI／CD 成为可能。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"VLPYS","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"728T0","text":"更好的支持服务治理"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"小点"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"第三，微服务架构可以使每个微服务独立部署。"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"LQVLU","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"EGSNL","text":"比如我们可以在 EC2 计算优化实例上部署 CPU 密集型服务，在 EC2 内存优化实例上部署内存数据库服务。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"UGJCF","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"5218N","text":"实现更高的并发"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"6IIK6","text":"更好的兼容云计算平台"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"小点"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"最后，微服务架构使得每个服务都可独立扩展。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"第一种角度","shrink":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"2UQ4M","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"G6674","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"14Y60","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"707WZ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"57ITT","text":"组件之间使用 REST API 进行通信，而 REST 是无状态的，所以可以水平扩展。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务可以分别有自己的分层架构和数据库，并且不限于使用相同的技术、框架和语言来开发这些服务。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"每个组件都是自主的，可以独立开发、构建、测试和部署。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"耦合性"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"M7351","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"05XI8","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"B2656","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"6GV85","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"GX1WG","text":"优化对资源的利用。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"服务内部还可以独立扩展。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"可以单独扩展那些需要扩展的服务。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"二维扩展"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"扩展性"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"O8O6X","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"7OS11","text":"只回滚那些出故障的服务不会影响其他服务。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"运维性"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"84NQD","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"7JBVT","text":"不会限制你使用特定的技术，提供了一种开发和工程活动的新范式。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"技术更新"},"4":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XBDYI","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"68QVX","text":"独立部署，系统隔离，降低了系统故障的风险"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"敏捷开发"},"5":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"55WDF","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"R8AKC","text":"面对更少量的代码注意力会更集中，实现新功能和新想法变得很容易。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"开发工作量"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"第二种角度","shrink":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的优点","shrink":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"QUFTC","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"RSKXT","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"QVCWC","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"WQVQU","text":"系统复杂、服务拆分的度不好把握。把握不好度或者滥用的话，这个模式适得其反！"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PCKOF","text":"业务逻辑应该按照什么规则划分为微服务，这本身就是一个经验工程。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"DVGCQ","text":"虽然建立小型服务是微服务架构崇尚的，但要记住，微服务是达到目的的手段，而不是目标。微服务的目标是充分分解应用程序，以促进敏捷开发和持续集成部署。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务强调了服务大小，但实际上这并没有一个统一的标准。","shrink":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ZDYXR","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ICJAE","text":"开发人员需要基于 RPC 或者消息实现微服务之间的调用和通信，而这就使得服务之间的发现、服务调用链的跟踪和质量问题变得的相当棘手。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务的分布式特点带来的复杂性。","shrink":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"SSYJK","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"JAJUJ","text":"CAP 原理的约束，使得我们不得不放弃传统的强一致性，而转而追求最终一致性，这个对开发人员来说是一个挑战。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"分区的数据库体系和分布式事务。","shrink":true},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YQWTT","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"DDLVS","text":"对微服务进行测试，需要启动它依赖的所有其他服务。这种复杂性不可低估。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构对测试也带来了很大的挑战。","shrink":true},"4":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"DGSPJ","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"VQOJJ","text":"在传统单体应用中，若有 A、B、C 三个服务需要更改，A 依赖 B，B 依赖 C。我们只需更改相应的模块，然后一次性部署即可。\n但是在微服务架构中，我们需要仔细规划和协调每个服务的变更部署。我们需要先更新 C，然后更新 B，最后更新 A。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务的另一大挑战是跨多个服务的更改。","shrink":true},"5":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"ESJZT","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"AIUKL","text":"微服务由不同的大量服务构成。每种服务可能拥有自己的配置、应用实例数量以及基础服务地址。这里就需要不同的配置、部署、扩展和监控组件。"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"CBKUQ","text":"我们还需要服务发现机制，以便服务可以发现与其通信的其他服务的地址。"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"AYELF","text":"因此，成功部署微服务应用需要开发人员有更好地部署策略和高度自动化的水平。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"部署基于微服务的应用也要复杂得多。","shrink":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"微服务架构的不足","remark":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qkXa3VszeMquhTodUtYMbQ","remarkDisplay":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"XNCL5","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"44I47","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"58C4E","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"SFN40","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"881GU","text":"服务频繁发布"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"复杂多变"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"6315C","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"4X0TK","text":"业务线相互耦合"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"逻辑混乱"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"66IEE","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"2D414","text":"数据单点依赖"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"难以扩展"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"GUL8E","text":"不敢下线"},"4":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"K3PRR","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"U7YH3","text":"小成本创新"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"创新探索"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"问题"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"84DG2","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"MKB35","text":"日志采集"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"8DRM8","text":"水平扩容"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"7251B","text":"数据库升级"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"41Z38","children":{"0":{"objectClass":